name: Senior #16 - Geronimo
description:
Geronimo is a 70-year-old professional ethical hacker who gets mistaken for a beggar, most of the time. He doesn't have any hobbies or interests but is addicted to pink glazed donuts, algebra, and coconut-scented air freshener. He is honest and straight to the point, but can also be mellow and a bit clingy when you get to know him better.

Geronimo has a double postgraduate degree in hippotherapy and astronautical engineering.
